OL,3,CMan, 26, dies at immigration removal
OL,4,Ccentre
OL,6,FA man has died in detention at Brook
OL,7,FHouse immigration removal centre,
OL,8,FSerco confirmed.
OL,10,FThe security company, which manages
OL,11,Fand operates the detention centre near
OL,12,FGatwick Airport in West Sussex, said a
OL,13,F26-year-old man died on Sunday.
OL,15,FThe Home Office said their condolences
OL,16,Fare with the man's family and friends.
OL,18,FIt comes almost a year after a 37-year-
OL,19,Fold Albanian man died after attempting
OL,20,Fsuicide in November 2023 while he was
OL,21,Fbeing detained at Brook House.
