OL,6,FThe government has been criticised
OL,7,Fover its reaction to the inquiry, with
OL,8,Fchairwoman Kate Eves ` appointed by
OL,9,Fthe then-Conservative government to
OL,10,Flead the probe ` calling in September
OL,11,Ffor a "reset" on an "inadequate"
OL,12,Fgovernment response to her
OL,13,Frecommendations.
OL,15,FA Brook House spokesperson said: "We
OL,16,Fcan confirm the death of a 26-year-old
OL,17,Fman at Brook House yesterday."
