OL,6,FThe Gatwick Detainees Welfare Group,
OL,7,Fwhich supports detainees at Brook
OL,8,FHouse, said "no one should take their
OL,9,Flast breath" at the centre.
OL,11,FPaying tribute to the man who died,
OL,12,Fthe charity said on X, formerly
OL,13,FTwitter: "On the death of a man in
OL,14,Fdetention yesterday we send heartfelt
OL,15,Fcondolences to his family, friends and
OL,16,Feveryone who knew and loved him.
OL,18,F"Brook House is prison architecture,
OL,19,Fand no-one should take their last
OL,20,Fbreath there. We mourn that a young
OL,21,Fman died before he could be free."
