OL,6,FSteve Valdez-Symonds, Amnesty
OL,7,FInternational UK's refugee and migrant
OL,8,Frights director, said: "We despair at
OL,9,Freports that yet another person has
OL,10,Fdied in the Brook House detention
OL,11,Fcentre. Our hearts go out to his
OL,12,Ffamily, friends and the fellow
OL,13,Fdetainees affected by this tragedy too.
OL,15,F"Brook House has gained notoriety for
OL,16,Fviolence, racism and abuse. What part
OL,17,Fthis may have in this man's death we
OL,18,Fdo not yet know, but these
OL,19,Fdegradations derive from a wider
OL,20,Ffailure to make a system respect human
OL,21,Fdignity and rights.
OL,26,@pD@XOUwD@AOU
