OL,6,F"Tragic incidents such as this
OL,7,Femphasise why the Government must
OL,8,Fbring humanity to the immigration
OL,9,Fsystem as much as any other policy
OL,10,Farea ` people's lives depend on it."
OL,12,FMedical Justice, which works with
OL,13,Fvulnerable people in immigration
OL,14,Fdetention, called immigration removal
OL,15,Fcentres (IRCs) "dangerous".
