OL,6,FThe charity made reference to Frank
OL,7,FOspina who died last March while he
OL,8,Fwas being detained at Colnbrook
OL,9,Fimmigration removal centre, in West
OL,10,FDrayton, Middlesex, pending his
OL,11,Fremoval to Colombia.
OL,13,FAn jury at an inquest into his death
OL,14,Ffound that he had died by suicide.
OL,16,FMedical Justice said: "Brook House
OL,17,FInquiry found clinical safeguards in
OL,18,Fdetention to be "dysfunctional" and
OL,19,Fthe systemic failures are ongoing.
