OL,6,F"Just a matter of days ago, in
OL,7,Fresponse to the inquest into the
OL,8,Fsuicide in immigration detention of
OL,9,FFrank Ospina following a catalogue of
OL,10,Ffailings in his care, the Home Office
OL,11,Fclaimed that it has taken a number of
OL,12,Factions to improve the safeguards for
OL,13,Findividuals in detention.
OL,15,F"Medical Justice has little confidence
OL,16,Fthis is the case as we have seen no
OL,17,Fimprovement in safety in detention
OL,18,Ffollowing many such assurances over
OL,19,Fthe years."
